===Adjective===
{{en-adj}}

# Like a [[pedant]], overly concerned with [[formal]] rules and [[trivial]] points of learning.
# Being [[showy]] of one’s [[knowledge]], often in a [[boring]] manner.
# Being [[finicky]] or [[fastidious]] with [[language]].

